  "title": "Clinic Assistant",
  "description": "<p>The Clinic Assistant will play a crucial role in managing the reception area, attending to patients, performing administrative tasks, and providing support to doctors during consultations. The duties and responsibilities include:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Manage the reception area, greeting patients, and handling phone calls professionally.</p>\n<p>Attend to patients and perform front-desk duties including registration, scheduling appointments, verifying insurance, and managing billing.</p>\n<p>Process insurance claims, handle Medisave transactions, and conduct regular stock-taking of medical supplies.</p>\n<p>Update billing records accurately and reconcile daily collections.</p>\n<p>Provide assistance to doctors during consultations, ensuring patients’ needs are met efficiently.</p>\n<p>Maintain a clean and organized clinic environment.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Requirements</p>\n<p>Experience in a healthcare setting would be advantageous.</p>\n<p>Excellent interpersonal and communication skills.</p>\n<p>Strong customer-service mindset with a focus on patient satisfaction.</p>\n<p>Ability to multitask and work efficiently in a fast-paced environment.</p>\n<p>Proficiency in medical billing software and basic computer skills.</p>",
